author: Barnini Chakraborty
title: Wuhan residents say coronavirus figures released by China don't add up
description: Chinese officials, desperate to recast the country as a global leader that has conquered the coronavirus, have been saying that its death rates are decreasing in the city of Wuhan. The problem, residents say, is that the numbers don't add up.
